article_title: Rep. Peter King: Vote shows ‘Ted Cruz is a fraud’

article_metadata.description: Video on NBCNews.com: Rep. Peter King (R-NY) explains why Republicans in the House were voting on a government funding bill that defunds Obamacare, saying “it will be a major step in letting people know that Ted Cruz is a fraud and he'll no longer have any influence in the Republican Party.”
